# Start profile
IMAPStore luca@keyfried.com-remote
Host mail.keyfried.com
Port 993
User luca@keyfried.com
PassCmd "pass hosts/spacehb/luca"
AuthMechs LOGIN
TLSType IMAPS
CertificateFile /etc/ssl/certs/ca-certificates.crt

MaildirStore luca@keyfried.com-local
Subfolders Verbatim
Path ~/.local/share/mail/luca@keyfried.com/
Inbox ~/.local/share/mail/luca@keyfried.com/INBOX

Channel luca@keyfried.com
Expunge Both
Far :luca@keyfried.com-remote:
Near :luca@keyfried.com-local:
Patterns * !"[Gmail]/All Mail" !"*fts-flatcurve*" !"*virtual*"
Create Both
SyncState *
MaxMessages 0
ExpireUnread no
# End profile

